  "title": "LOOKING FOR PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<ul><li>Lead project implementation using appropriate project management methodologies, standards, and tools to drive and facilitate successful project delivery.</li><li>Lead requirements gathering with stakeholders.</li><li>Ensure the assigned project meets requirement targets, aligns with the organization's strategic objectives, and adheres to best practices.</li><li>Implement effective governance processes for project acceptance based on sound business cases.</li><li>Provide the project owner with the information needed to assess which proposals have the highest potential value, impact, and strategic alignment.</li><li>Oversee project KPIs, monitor performance against standards, and take timely corrective actions.</li><li>Review project schedules, quality, and cost deliverables.</li><li>Regularly monitor and report project performance and progress to all stakeholders.</li><li>Coordinate documentation and administration for the assigned project.</li><li>Proactively handle administrative tasks independently (e.g., follow-ups from meetings, scheduling, taking minutes, compiling requirements, etc.).</li></ul>",
